{"tid":2098307,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國內國安法又拉人啦","createTime":"2020-07-07T11:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T06:52:06.000Z","uid":131875,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0bbea080b26078beea272bb8274f0b1d0340e20f","tid":2098307,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BeiMingRFA/status/1280148753706635265?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBeiMingRFA%2Fstatus%2F1280148753706635265%3Fs%3D20&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivcE4f%2F6cKlXs%2FdqEvpC7bjY%3D&h=1dd9a95b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBeiMingRFA%2Fstatus%2F1280148753706635265%3Fs%3D20&h=fe6db05c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BeiMingRFA/status/1280148753706635265?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"1d566b8750132f7556bde5f8350c2bb06410ab66","tid":2098307,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"532edea2a27a73fd3b08545b6599659d8271ba25","tid":2098307,"uid":38182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091bfed84e33809b8e4803a3c524136c7ade3004","tid":2098307,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"佢篇文尾段<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上九點，呈諸國民，均為常識。而一再申說，就在於國家治理未入常態政治軌道，國族政治文明有待現代轉型，而於積善前行中，期期以&ldquo;立憲民主，人民共和&rdquo;收束這波已然延續一個半世紀的文明大轉型。正是在此，我們，&ldquo;我們人民&rdquo;，豈能&ldquo;豬一般的苟且，狗一樣的奴媚，蛆蟲似的卑污&rdquo;?!<br />\n<br />\n行文至此，回瞰身後，戊戌以來，在下因言獲罪，降級停職，留校察看，行止困限。此番作文，預感必有新罰降身，抑或竟為筆者此生最後一文，亦未可知。但大疫當前，前有溝壑，則言責在身，不可推諉，無所逃遁。否則，不如殺豬賣肉。是的，義憤，如西哲所言，正是義憤，惟義與憤所在，惟吾土先賢揭櫫之仁與義這一&ldquo;人心人路&rdquo;之激盪，令書齋學者成為知識分子，直至把性命搭進去。畢竟，自由，一種超驗存在和行動指歸，一種最具神性的世界現象，是人之為人的禀賦，華夏兒女不能例外。而世界精神，那個地上的神，不是別的，就是自由理念的絢爛展開。如此，朋友，我的億萬同胞，縱然火湖在前，何所懼哉!"},{"pid":"2abc0ca2f8ad5ec4fd7841977cc93346d3612bb1","tid":2098307,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"真手足，都唔知有無命翻出黎"},{"pid":"b6ea2680bdb9443f7b200ba1d04508f90d274d77","tid":2098307,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"人地大陸人都敢發聲<br />\ndelete twitter 班淆底獸係咪要感到羞恥"},{"pid":"14445c407923f89fdcb6cc920009a398405d3470","tid":2098307,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"順我者昌，逆我者 嫖娼！"},{"pid":"d569e7395719f7f2d75b0897580b5809e4400e13","tid":2098307,"uid":253223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"支那應該search 唔到佢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266e675ee27fc591aaac7202d8d674f2350af192","tid":2098307,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14445c407923f89fdcb6cc920009a398405d3470","tid":2098307,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"順我者昌，逆我者 嫖娼！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:10:10.000Z","msg":"教授住北京 <br />\n被控遙距到四川叫雞"},{"pid":"acd56b7e0b60fe0311bad339390009b6edad09a6","tid":2098307,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14445c407923f89fdcb6cc920009a398405d3470","tid":2098307,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"順我者昌，逆我者 嫖娼！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"逆我者娼，順我者忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b509122262781455ad68a67d40cacf34a78c2e","tid":2098307,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hildevautmans/status/1280419757578235904?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhildevautmans%2Fstatus%2F1280419757578235904%3Fs%3D20&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2